{
  "stem": "5470.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I wasn't actually free until the train had left the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Therefore, I know, so now everybody is safe whom I have to take care for.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were from several organizations that [? fire, ?] [? fire. ?] Then it came to [? know ?] to me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some times I got it in a piece of paper, small paper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes just by mouth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the-- in one of the transports, that was, that was the particular transport where these people were put into a barrack and then straight away re-registered outside the camp into the train.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was one of my, my personnel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I couldn't get him out anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he was already in for the register.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If he would have been-- before that, I could have perhaps saved him, at that particular time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he was already registered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's where I saw him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, you know, well, I can't do anything anymore. and he said, OK.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Would you be so kind and post that postcard for me that my family knows that I'm out of the country, or going out of the country.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, certainly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I picked up the card and put it-- wanted to put it in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then one of the Dutch policeman was standing behind me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Picked it out of my hand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, what are you doing there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, what are you looking after me for?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Huh?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so before I was actually-- after the transfer, back into my office, the message boy from the German camp commander sent over him to me if I wanted to come into his office by a certain time, 12 o'clock or something.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went into his office, and--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first-- he had a coat.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
